			<h1 class="page-title">Minor in Arabic</h1>



<div id="textcontainer" class="page_content">

<div class="sidebar">
	<div id="sidebar-contact">








	</div>
</div>

<p>To earn the Minor in Arabic, students musts complete 19 semester hours (12 of which must be at the 200 level or above) as follows:</p>
